{"tid":195600,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"夏天即將來臨  大汗撚請入","createTime":"2017-04-10T17:15:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-08T08:01:48.000Z","uid":15174,"like":14,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"46355fce8c59b21e9accc6528a0715fdc404a3e3","tid":195600,"uid":15174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:15:19.000Z","msg":"宜家即使未到夏天<br />\n但係到中午太陽曬住您頭頂<br />\n返工返學又要同咁多人迫<br />\n唔多唔少都一定會出汗<br />\n少汗都還好  啲大汗撚就真係搞唔撚掂<br />\n<br />\n到底大汗撚夏天係咪真係應該留喺屋企<br />\n邊到都唔好去？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 每個人都會出汗  無所謂嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 留返喺屋企咪撚出街搞臭人啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：大汗撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a98066959cc9a614a1b0d71c23748162013bbff","tid":195600,"uid":42766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:17:08.000Z","msg":"有無人做過汗線果啲治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   想去做格拉底"},{"pid":"039bbc3a3e4fe2bb177a9cf891d2dfeacd8b7f98","tid":195600,"uid":15174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:17:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無人做過汗線果啲治療<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />   想去做格拉底</blockquote><br />\n我全身都想做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad212979b16ee6d63c26fe49bd2fdce29d96ea76","tid":195600,"uid":83004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:19:28.000Z","msg":"男友好大汗<br />\n一出室外就出汗<br />\n一出汗佢就唔耐煩想發脾氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea5428b8cdf2b5fc3a4501e8ca3e7be9f78dbe8a","tid":195600,"uid":15174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T17:20:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男友好大汗<br />\n一出室外就出汗<br />\n一出汗佢就唔耐煩想發脾氣<img